{"word":"H4772 - מַרְגְלָה - margᵉlâh - mar-ghel-aw' - Feet","slug":"H4772","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מַרְגְלָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>margᵉlâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mar-ghel-aw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Feet"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05E8;&#x05D2;&#x05BC;&#x05DC;&#x05D4; - marg<sup>e</sup>la&#x0302;h</b> - <i>mar-ghel-aw'</i><p/>Denominative from <a href=\"#/H7272\">H7272</a>; (plural for collective) a <i>foot piece</i>, that is, (adverbially) <i>at the foot</i>, or (directly) the <i>foot</i> itself: - feet. Compare <a href=\"#/H4763\">H4763</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7270\">H7270</a>, <a href=\"#/H7272\">H7272</a>, <a href=\"#/H7273\">H7273</a>, <a href=\"#/H7274\">H7274</a>, <a href=\"#/H8637\">H8637</a>"}]}